  stimulus_text = 'A scientist is writing a report for a scientific journal. In the report, the scientist describes an experiment that was conducted to test the effectiveness of a new type of fertilizer. The scientist wants to make sure that the report is clear and concise. Which of the following sentences from the scientist’s report should be revised to improve the clarity and conciseness of the report?',
